cast.overview: When larcenous real estate clerk Marion Crane goes on the lam with a wad of cash and hopes of starting a new life, she ends up at the notorious Bates Motel, where manager Norman Bates cares for his housebound mother.
cast.title: Psycho

cast.overview: Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.
cast.title: Citizen Kane
cast.character: Woman in Front of Chronicle Building (uncredited)

details.biography: Born Lillian Wilkes, Lillian O’Malley was a character actress who started her career in minor roles during the 1930s and was most frequently seen in western movies playing supporting bit parts. She married silent film star and fellow but part player Pat O’Malley, with whom she had three daughters.
details.name: Lillian O'Malley
